headline.main: Sushi in Pyongyang: Japanese Chef Opens Rare Restaurant
headline.print_headline: Sushi in Pyongyang: Japanese Chef Opens Rare Restaurant

lead_paragraph: Sushi in Pyongyang? At a restaurant run by a Japanese sushi chef famous for working for North Korea's late leader Kim Jong Il?
